\pard\sa300\sl240\slmult1\b The Management of Access Controls\b0\~for super administrative rights of operating systems (known as the \ldblquote root\rdblquote  level access) is a substantial challenge for any IT controls environment. It prevents unauthorized access to key systems and databases because:\par

